Usage: change_IB_cell_site_name [-help] [-NF <string>] [-NNF <string>]
                                [-PF <string>] [-PPF <string>] [-new <string>]
                                [-original <string>] [-vertical]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-NF <string>                  # specify site name of N-filler cell
                              # (string, optional)
-NNF <string>                 # specify site name of NN-filler cell
                              # (string, optional)
-PF <string>                  # specify site name of P-filler cell
                              # (string, optional)
-PPF <string>                 # specify site name of PP-filler cell
                              # (string, optional)
-new <string>                 # specify new site name of IB cell
                              # (string, optional)
-original <string>            # specify original site name of IB cell.
                              # (string, optional)
-vertical                     # is vertical IB transform (bool, optional)